倫敦南岸大學的畢業生起始工資水平為全英第六高。<ref name="sal-times">[http://extras.timesonline.co.uk/pdfs/highestgraduatestartingsalaries.pdf Highest Graduate Starting Salaries] {{Wayback|url=http://extras.timesonline.co.uk/pdfs/highestgraduatestartingsalaries.pdf |date=20110705082702 }}, ''[[Sunday_Times_University_Guide|Sunday Times University Guide]]'', 2011.</ref> 2013年衛報大學指南將其列在119所英國教育機構中的113位。<ref>{{cite news|title=University guide 2013: University league table|url=http://www.theguardian.com/education/table/2013/jun/03/university-league-table-2014|work=The Guardian|publisher=Guardian News & Media Ltd|accessdate=30 December 2013|location=London|date=3 June 2013|archive-date=2020-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200831084602/https://www.theguardian.com/education/table/2013/jun/03/university-league-table-2014|dead-url=no}}</ref> 星期天泰晤士大學指南將之列在122所教育結構中的115位。<ref>{{cite news|title=The Times University Guide|url=http://extras.timesonline.co.uk/stug/universityguide.php|work=TLS - Times Literary Supplement|publisher=Times Newspapers Ltd|accessdate=20 August 2010|location=London|deadurl=yes|first=Anushka|last=Asthana|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100522133308/http://extras.timesonline.co.uk/stug/universityguide.php|archivedate=2010年5月22日}}</ref>

